---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout>
  <section class="hero" style="padding-bottom: 2rem;">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <h1 class="hero__title">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="hero__sub mx-auto">Last Updated: February 2026</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section style="padding-top: 2rem; padding-bottom: 6rem;">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; color: var(--clr-text-sub); line-height: 1.8;">
      <h2 style="color: var(--clr-text); font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
        By accessing or using the RAGBase platform ("Service"), you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you are using the Service on behalf of an organization (such as a law firm, financial institution, or healthcare provider), you represent that you have the authority to bind that organization to these terms.
      </p>

      <h2 style="color: var(--clr-text); font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">2. Scope of Service and Disclaimers</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
        RAGBase provides an AI-powered research and synthesis platform. <strong>Important Disclaimer:</strong> RAGBase is a research tool, not a human professional. We do not provide legal, financial, or medical advice.<br><br>
        All outputs generated by RAGBase must be reviewed, verified, and approved by qualified professionals before use in any official capacity. RAGBase is not liable for errors, omissions, or misinterpretations arising from the use of the Service.
      </p>

      <h2 style="color: var(--clr-text); font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">3. User Responsibilities</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
        You are responsible for the legality, reliability, and appropriateness of the documents you upload. You agree not to upload data that violates third-party rights or applicable laws. While RAGBase employs a PII Redaction Firewall, you remain the ultimate data controller.
      </p>

      <h2 style="color: var(--clr-text); font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">4. Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
        The Service, including its original content, multi-agent architecture, and design, are and will remain the exclusive property of RAGBase. Your uploaded documents and the specific text queries you input remain your exclusive property.
      </p>

      <h2 style="color: var(--clr-text); font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">5. Contact</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
        For legal obligations, contract updates, or to report a violation of these terms, please contact us at: <a href="mailto:contact@ragbasehq.com" style="color: var(--clr-primary); text-decoration: underline;">contact@ragbasehq.com</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
